cc:Work.dc:title: Comic Book Cover
cc:Work.dc:description: A comic book cover depicting a robot shooting laser beams from its eyes at a masked running woman. Text (as paths) reads, "No. 1 March Stupefaction Comics Fantastic Escapades Featuring the exciting new action character Jade Feline! 10¢ In this issue — Can Jade Feline stop rampaging robot from wreaking mayhem and havoc?" and is derived from fonts (Rammetto One, Patrick Hand, Dosis, and Leckerli One) available under the SIL Open Font License
